[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gavin Horne named as Llanellen Bridge fatal crash pedestrian

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The pedestrian who died following a car crash in Monmouthshire has been named by police.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gavin Horne, 37, from Caerphilly, died following the incident involving a Seat Ibiza on the A4042, near Llanellen Bridge, at about 11:50 BST on Monday.
The road was closed while Gwent Police investigated, but has since reopened.
